				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Since the release of OoW, I've had it happen on many occasions when someone I summon is clearly more than 200 feet away isn't removed from the hate list of mobs. There are no DoT's involved either. An example of this is right now when I was in SolA with a twinked warrior of mine. I was mainly soloing with him, but kept mage around too in case I had to ghetto evac. What annoyed me was that when I summoned my warrior to the other end of the dungeon, mobs still ran all the way up and brought a few friends, the aggro was still there.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=597626">Enharjaren Fenrirsbane</a> 
